                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>General
                    </button>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                    <button class="nav-link" id="booking-tab" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#booking" type="button" role="tab">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt me-2"></i>Booking
                    </button>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                    <button class="nav-link" id="payment-tab" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#payment" type="button" role="tab">
                        <i class="fas fa-credit-card me-2"></i>Payment
                    </button>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                    <button class="nav-link" id="policies-tab" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#policies" type="button" role="tab">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-contract me-2"></i>Policies
                    </button>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ Content -->
<div class="container mb-5">
    <div class="tab-content" id="faqTabContent">
        <!-- General FAQ -->
        <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="general" role="tabpanel">
            <div class="accordion" id="generalAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="general1">
                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#generalCollapse1">
                            What documents do I need to rent a car?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="generalCollapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#generalAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>To rent a car, you'll need:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Valid driver's license (minimum 1 year old)</li>
                                <li>Government-issued photo ID (passport, national ID)</li>
                                <li>Credit card for security deposit</li>
                                <li>Proof of identity (NIC/passport)</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>International visitors need a valid international driving permit along with their home country license.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="general2">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#generalCollapse2">
                            What is the minimum age requirement to rent a car?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="generalCollapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#generalAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>The minimum age to rent a car is <strong>21 years old</strong>.</p>
                            <p>Additional conditions:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Drivers aged 21-24: Young driver surcharge may apply</li>
                                <li>Drivers aged 25+: Full access to all vehicle categories</li>
                                <li>Driver must have held a valid license for at least 1 year</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="general3">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#generalCollapse3">
                            What types of vehicles do you offer?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="generalCollapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#generalAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>We offer a diverse fleet including:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Economy Cars:</strong> Fuel-efficient compact vehicles</li>
                                <li><strong>Sedans:</strong> Comfortable mid-size and full-size cars</li>
                                <li><strong>SUVs:</strong> Spacious vehicles for families and groups</li>
                                <li><strong>Luxury Cars:</strong> Premium vehicles for special occasions</li>
                                <li><strong>Convertibles:</strong> Open-top driving experience</li>
                                <li><strong>Electric Vehicles:</strong> Eco-friendly options</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="general4">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#generalCollapse4">
                            Do you provide 24/7 customer support?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="generalCollapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#generalAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Yes! We provide round-the-clock customer support.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Emergency Support:</strong> 24/7 roadside assistance</li>
                                <li><strong>Phone Support:</strong> Available during business hours</li>
                                <li><strong>Online Support:</strong> Contact form and live chat</li>
                                <li><strong>Email Support:</strong> Response within 24 hours</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Booking FAQ -->
