            <div class="accordion" id="bookingAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="booking1">
                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#bookingCollapse1">
                            How do I make a reservation?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="bookingCollapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#bookingAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Making a reservation is easy:</p>
                            <ol>
                                <li>Browse our available cars</li>
                                <li>Select your preferred vehicle</li>
                                <li>Choose pickup and return dates</li>
                                <li>Provide required documentation</li>
                                <li>Pay advance amount (50% of total cost)</li>
                                <li>Receive confirmation email</li>
                            </ol>
                            <p>You can book online through our website or visit our office.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="booking2">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#bookingCollapse2">
                            Can I modify or cancel my reservation?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="bookingCollapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#bookingAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p><strong>Modifications:</strong></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Free modifications up to 24 hours before pickup</li>
                                <li>Subject to vehicle availability</li>
                                <li>Price difference may apply</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p><strong>Cancellations:</strong></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Free cancellation up to 24 hours before pickup</li>
                                <li>Full refund of advance payment</li>
                                <li>Late cancellations may incur charges</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="booking3">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#bookingCollapse3">
                            How far in advance can I book?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="bookingCollapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#bookingAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>You can book:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Up to 6 months in advance</strong> for guaranteed availability</li>
                                <li><strong>Same-day bookings</strong> subject to availability</li>
                                <li><strong>Last-minute reservations</strong> possible but not guaranteed</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>We recommend booking at least 3-7 days in advance for popular dates and seasons.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="booking4">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#bookingCollapse4">
                            What happens if the car is not available?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="bookingCollapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#bookingAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>If your reserved car is unavailable:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>We'll offer a similar or upgraded vehicle at no extra cost</li>
                                <li>Full refund if no suitable alternative is available</li>
                                <li>Immediate notification via email/phone</li>
                                <li>Priority rebooking for future dates</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Payment FAQ -->
        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="payment" role="tabpanel">
            <div class="accordion" id="paymentAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="payment1">
                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#paymentCollapse1">
                            What payment methods do you accept?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="paymentCollapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#paymentAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>We accept various payment methods:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Credit Cards:</strong> Visa, MasterCard, American Express</li>
                                <li><strong>Debit Cards:</strong> Major bank cards</li>
                                <li><strong>Online Payment:</strong> Secure payment gateway</li>
                                <li><strong>Bank Transfer:</strong> Direct bank transfers</li>
                                <li><strong>Cash:</strong> At pickup location</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="payment2">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#paymentCollapse2">
                            When do I need to pay?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="paymentCollapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#paymentAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p><strong>Payment Schedule:</strong></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Advance Payment:</strong> 50% at booking confirmation</li>
                                <li><strong>Remaining Payment:</strong> At vehicle pickup</li>
                                <li><strong>Security Deposit:</strong> Refundable amount at pickup</li>
                                <li><strong>Extra Charges:</strong> At vehicle return (if applicable)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="payment3">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#paymentCollapse3">
                            Is there a security deposit?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="paymentCollapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#paymentAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Yes, a refundable security deposit is required:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Amount:</strong> Varies by vehicle category</li>
                                <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> Cover potential damages or extra charges</li>
                                <li><strong>Hold Method:</strong> Credit card authorization</li>
                                <li><strong>Refund:</strong> Released within 7-10 business days after return</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="payment4">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#paymentCollapse4">
                            Are there any hidden fees?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="paymentCollapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#paymentAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>We believe in transparent pricing with no hidden fees:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Base Rental Rate:</strong> Clearly displayed</li>
                                <li><strong>Taxes:</strong> Included in final price</li>
