                                <li><strong>Hourly Rate:</strong> Charged for each additional hour</li>
                                <li><strong>Full Day:</strong> Charged if more than 4 hours late</li>
                                <li><strong>Notification:</strong> Contact us if delay is expected</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item faq-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="policies4">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#policiesCollapse4">
                            Can someone else drive the rental car?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="policiesCollapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#policiesAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p><strong>Additional Driver Policy:</strong></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Additional drivers must be authorized at booking</li>
                                <li>Must meet same requirements as primary driver</li>
                                <li>Additional driver fee may apply</li>
                                <li>All drivers must be present at pickup</li>
                                <li>Spouse/partner may be covered under certain conditions</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

